480
00:35:28,960 --> 00:35:31,960
Per tant, crec que de calories estic ingerint la suficients.

481
00:35:32,960 --> 00:35:34,960
Prens algun suplement?

482
00:35:34,960 --> 00:35:37,960
Sí, prenc un suplement de vitamines genèric,

483
00:35:37,960 --> 00:35:39,960
