488
00:35:52,960 --> 00:35:54,960
Pregunta. No, no.

489
00:35:54,960 --> 00:35:56,960
Intento menjar variat i...

490
00:35:56,960 --> 00:35:58,960
De tant en quant, que us dic,

491
00:35:58,960 --> 00:36:00,960
