492
00:36:00,960 --> 00:36:03,960
O vaig a un restaurant i menjo algú de verdures.

493
00:36:03,960 --> 00:36:05,960
Com em dutxo?

494
00:36:05,960 --> 00:36:07,960
Doncs no em dutxo.

495
00:36:07,960 --> 00:36:09,960
Em dutxo només quan estic aquí a hotels,

496
00:36:09,960 --> 00:36:11,960
